domain

Class Chromosome

  • java.lang.Object
    • domain.Chromosome

  • public class Chromosome
extends java.lang.Object
    Chromosome is the domain object of Application. It is the naive model of a real chromosome(in biology) All fields are made private to hide the details of implementation from outer classes. They are accessible through public methods.
